---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact"
  description="oozoofrog.dev 블로그 운영자에게 연락하기"
>
  <article class="contact-page">
    <h1>Contact</h1>

    <section>
      <h2>연락처</h2>
      <p>블로그에 대한 문의, 피드백, 또는 협업 제안이 있으시면 아래 방법으로 연락해 주세요.</p>

      <div class="contact-cards">
        <a href="mailto:oozoofrog@gmail.com" class="contact-card">
          <span class="contact-icon">✉</span>
          <span class="contact-label">Email</span>
          <span class="contact-value">oozoofrog@gmail.com</span>
        </a>

        <a href="https://github.com/oozoofrog" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-card">
          <span class="contact-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 0C3.58 0 0 3.58 0 8c0 3.54 2.29 6.53 5.47 7.59.4.07.55-.17.55-.38 0-.19-.01-.82-.01-1.49-2.01.37-2.53-.49-2.69-.94-.09-.23-.48-.94-.82-1.13-.28-.15-.68-.52-.01-.53.63-.01 1.08.58 1.23.82.72 1.21 1.87.87 2.33.66.07-.52.28-.87.51-1.07-1.78-.2-3.64-.89-3.64-3.95 0-.87.31-1.59.82-2.15-.08-.2-.36-1.02.08-2.12 0 0 .67-.21 2.2.82.64-.18 1.32-.27 2-.27.68 0 1.36.09 2 .27 1.53-1.04 2.2-.82 2.2-.82.44 1.1.16 1.92.08 2.12.51.56.82 1.27.82 2.15 0 3.07-1.87 3.75-3.65 3.95.29.25.54.73.54 1.48 0 1.07-.01 1.93-.01 2.2 0 .21.15.46.55.38A8.013 8.013 0 0016 8c0-4.42-3.58-8-8-8z"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span class="contact-label">GitHub</span>
          <span class="contact-value">@oozoofrog</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>사이트 소개</h2>
      <p>oozoofrog.dev는 iOS/Swift 개발을 중심으로 한 기술 블로그입니다. 모바일 앱 개발, 프로그래밍 언어, 컴퓨터 과학 관련 주제를 다루고 있습니다.</p>
    </section>

    <nav class="page-nav">
      <a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a>
      <a href="/privacy/" class="nav-link">Privacy Policy</a>
    </nav>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .contact-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(150%);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(150%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
  }

  @supports not (backdrop-filter: blur(20px)) {
    .contact-page {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
    }
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.2em;
    color: var(--dark-green);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
    border-bottom: 3px solid var(--frog-green);
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.5em;
    color: var(--dark-green);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 16px;
  }

  h2::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 4px;
    height: 1.2em;
    background: var(--frog-green);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  p {
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .contact-cards {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .contact-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 24px 32px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #333;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 200px;
  }

  .contact-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-color: var(--frog-green);
  }

  .contact-icon {
    font-size: 1.5em;
    color: var(--frog-green);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .contact-icon svg {
    fill: var(--frog-green);
  }

  .contact-label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark-green);
    font-size: 1.1em;
  }

  .contact-value {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 0.9em;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--frog-green);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid transparent;
    transition: color 0.2s ease, border-bottom 0.2s ease;
  }

  a:hover {
    color: var(--planet-orange);
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--planet-orange);
  }

  .page-nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 60px;
    padding-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid #e0ebe6;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .nav-link {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    background: rgba(112, 168, 80, 0.75);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    color: #fff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(45, 80, 22, 0.15), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .nav-link:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    background: rgba(112, 168, 80, 0.85);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(45, 80, 22, 0.25), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  }

  @supports not (backdrop-filter: blur(12px)) {
    .nav-link {
      background: rgba(112, 168, 80, 0.9);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .contact-page {
      padding: 24px 16px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 1.8em;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.3em;
    }

    .contact-cards {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .page-nav {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .nav-link {
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
